  "texts": [
    "Figure 2 illustrates the PRISMA flow diagram, which describes the study selection process.",
    "Upon removing duplicates, a total of 2172 studies were identified through comprehensive literature searches of electronic databases and grey literature.",
    "Following title and abstract screening, 2121 studies were excluded, and 51 fulltext studies were retrieved for full-text review.",
    "Among these 51 studies, 38 were excluded due to the absence of any one or more of the following three inclusion criteria: (i) using AI in the VRehab platform; (ii) evaluating the platform within a patient population; and (iii) evaluating the platform at home.",
    "This resulted in the inclusion of 13 studies."
  ],
